metadata.name: Entangled Roses
metadata.description:
“Entangled Roses” is an animation depicting two women or (maybe more) embracing and kissing each other in a lake.
A large body of water symbolizes the unconscious mind, as we cannot see the depths of it. Here we may perhaps get a glimpse of the depths of their minds and emotions, what is surfacing when they are alone together. The darkness often symbolizes our shadows, memories and things we do not like about ourselves. The red roses meaning love and passion, is one of them remembering a past love ? Has her subconscious mind betrayed her as she is kissing her new love ? Is this love or passion ? 

“Entangled Roses” was created as a part of the "Love is Louder" collection curated by @OdysseyOfTheHeart.

Ai Animation + PR
